N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 37.8 - Radio-telephone utilities and resellers of telephone service

State Regulations

Applications pursuant to section
101
of the

Public Service Law by radio-telephone utilities and resellers of telephone
services need contain only a description of the securities to be issued and the
purposes for which the issuance is sought. Notes
